00:12:16,580 --> 00:12:17,900
Ale presne 3 minúty!

210
00:12:17,900 --> 00:12:19,800
Ohriať to presne na 3 minúty je kľúčové.

211
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:23,000
Oh! Už sa to otáča!

212
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:49,700
A presne takto

213
